description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Salar de Uyuni before sunset
-Waterside Forest
-Aloe Dikotoma Woods
-Frozen spring water
-Great Blue Hole
-Lake side in autumn
-Japanese old houses with snow at night
-Jewelry ice washed ashore
-Moss Forest in Yakushima island
-Glow above the waterfall
name: Fantastic Scenery
